race.description: Pirtek Muswellbrook Country Boosted Mdn Hcp
race.comment: PENA PALACE (4) has not raced since failing on a heavy track on debut over 1200m at Canterbury in July. Meets a thin line-up today so a better run is expected. ARAPAWA (3) was in commission but failed to produce on debut nine days ago over 1200m at Coonabarabran. Draws a much better gate and the blinkers go on so improvement is on the cards. EDDIE'S CHARM (6) raced wide but still managed to close the race off well and finish third over this course and distance recently. Ready to peak at the third run back. BRIDEGO (2) showed pace but tired in the closing stages to miss a placing on debut here at this distance last start. Draws far closer this time so there might be a bit more in the tank at the end of this. REDFORD RIVER (1) found 1000m at Taree a bit slick on debut. Can improve over a bit more ground.
